<br>
All of that being said, I'd suggest wizard.  You can teleport at least, and get to different parts of the world.  You have spells, as you were seeking, and can solo (I know of wizards who have soloed quite high) but you are still far better in a group.  And real wizard nuking is far too lacking in most places I've seen.  Nuking druids, sure.  A reasonable amount of mages, etc., and even enough clerics you sometimes see clerics turning DD when there are two or three in a group, but no one really touches wizards when it comes to this.  More wizards would be most welcome.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps.<br>
<br>
